### TaskMe API Testing
### Gunakan file ini untuk testing API dengan VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:9561/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:9561/health

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "full_name": "Test User"
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Profile (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Profile (requires token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Updated Test User",
  "avatar_url": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### Get Users (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Team (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Development Team",
  "description": "Team untuk pengembangan aplikasi"
}

### Get User Teams (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Team by ID (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams/team-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Team Members (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams/team-id-here/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add Team Member (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/teams/team-id-here/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-id-here",
  "role": "member"
}

### Create Project (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Project",
  "description": "Proyek sample untuk testing",
  "team_id": "team-id-here",
  "start_date": "2024-01-01",
  "end_date": "2024-12-31"
}

### Get User Projects (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Project Tasks (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/project/project-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Task (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/project/project-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Task",
  "description": "Tugas sample untuk testing",
  "priority": "medium",
  "estimated_hours": 8
}

### Get Task Statuses (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/statuses/project/project-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Notifications (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Unread Count (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Dashboard Analytics (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Change Password (requires token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_password": "password123",
  "new_password": "newpassword123"
}

### Logout (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
